title: Zenland
author: Zenland
created_time: December 28, 2022, 02:31:43 PMLast edit: May 17, 2023, 09:05:07 AM by Zenland
content: Happy upcoming New Year from the Zenland team! We wish you a new year filled with joy, success, and growth. To share the holiday vibes, everyone who signs up on Zenland for the first time gets $10 to their balance to pay the service fee whenever they use our escrow service. To claim the bonus, simply log in to Zenland using your Metamask, and PM your Metamask wallet address here on Bitcointalk. The offer is valid until Jan 10th. Disclaimer. The giveaway funds are not withdrawable.
